---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/index.css";
import "../styles/about.css";
---

<Layout>
<div class="about-page">
  <div class="about-container">
    <img class="about-image" src="/AboutWill.webp" alt="Will Donnell" />
    <div class="about-right">
      <header class="about-header">
        <span class="about-header__name">Will Donnell</span>
      </header>
      <div class="about-text body-copy">
        <p style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold">I'm Will! Great to meet you.</p>
        <p class="indent-first">I’m a graphic designer based in Dallas and I believe design changes lives. I’m passionate about the intersection of creativity and communication; throw in a campaign to rally behind and we can create something impossible to ignore.</p>
        <p class="indent-first">I design because it lets me communicate something more powerful than myself, collaborate with other creative people, and make the world better. Most of my experience lives in faith-based spaces — I love blending artistic function and creative service with the life-changing news of Jesus.</p>
        <p class="indent-first">I love people, Diet Coke with lime, dancefloors, movies, wired headphones, Jesus, serif typefaces, and This Love by Maroon 5.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center">Let's make something.</p>
        <div class="body-copy__links">
          <a href="mailto:hello@willdonnell.com">email</a>
          <a href="https://instagram.com/wlldnnll" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">instagram</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/willdonnell8/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin</a>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">&#8592;  back</a>
        <div class="about-overlay__gifs" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="/Gifs/framesbutton.gif" alt="">
          <img src="/Gifs/hedied4u.gif" alt="">
          <img src="/Gifs/macos8button.gif" alt="">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</Layout>
